{
  "stem": "10572.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They cannot defame us, and they cannot degrade us unless we degrade ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was, at that time, I thought, a kind of terrific morale booster for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And maybe this attitude toward the yellow [NON-ENGLISH], that we turned it into a positive-- was a reflection of our youthful idealism, our naivete, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it helped us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think we became more mature faster through these pressures that were working on us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Until they-- and-- and as I look back and try to answer your question, I did not ever suffer from unbearable anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But when-- when this thing happened to us in-- in May 1938, and we liquidated our downtown location, and took our workshop into our home and continued to-- continued our custom-made-- and had one designer and had maybe 15 loyal workers that stayed with us.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had among those only one Nazi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Among-- among the 50 coat-makers, we had only one that we knew was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe he was from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he couldn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But he always talked about the-- in-- in his funny dialect, that the Germans cannot have their own Fuhrer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have to bring him from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, he felt there was a bond between him and-- and Hitler.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was not made very, very welcome and happy in our workshop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All the other workers somehow had a distance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in-- in-- in-- in-- in the summer of 1938, I started to do some very serious soul-- soul-searching and-- and thinking of how we could get out of this dead-end street.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
